+$ cargo test
+all workspace tests passed (new tests: pnt-ephemeris 5/5, pnt-predictor 3/3)
+$ cargo clippy --all-targets -- -D warnings
+finished successfully, zero warnings
+$ cargo fmt --all -- --check
+finished successfully
